le est-elle identique &agrave; l&rsquo;adresse du si&egrave;ge social ? &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Oui &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Non </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:13pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;"><span style="color:#2e74b5"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Document(s) &agrave; fournir</span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:13pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;"><span style="color:#2e74b5"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span style="color:black">Merci de t&eacute;l&eacute;charger les documents ci-dessous :</span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Document officiel justifiant de l&#39;existence de l&#39;Entreprise et dat&eacute; de moins de 3 mois </span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Ex : Pour la France, extrait K-bis de moins de 3 mois</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;"><span style="color:#1f4d78"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Etape 3/4</span></span></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:13pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;"><span style="color:#2e74b5"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">Informations bancaires</span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style="font-size:13pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Calibri Light&quot;"><span style="color:#2e74b5"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><span style="color:black">Attention&nbsp;:</span></span></span